<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7507421>
    dc:description "Figs 1-3: Habitus from dorsal: (1) Syzeuctus laoticus nov.sp. ♀ holotype (HT); (2) S. siamensis nov.sp. ♀ HT; (3) S. orientalis nov.sp. ♁ paratype (PT)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7507421/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7507423>
    dc:description "Figs 4-9: Basal tergites from dorsal: (4) Syzeuctus achterbergi nov.sp. ♀ HT; (5) S. floresiensis nov.sp. ♀ HT; (6) S. genator nov.sp. ♀ HT; (7) S. laoticus nov.sp. ♀ HT; (8) S. orientalis nov.sp. ♁ PT; (9) S. siamensis nov.sp. ♀ HT." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7507423/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7507427>
    dc:description "Figs 10-15: Faces from frontal: (10) Syzeuctus achterbergi nov.sp. ♀ HT; (11) S. floresiensis nov.sp. ♀ HT; (12) S. genator nov.sp. ♀ HT; (13) S. laoticus nov.sp. ♀ HT; (14) S. orientalis nov.sp. ♁ HT; (15) S. siamensis nov.sp. ♀ HT." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7507427/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

